2. The 17th day of November 2023 is appointed as the day on which the 

Wildlife (Amendment) Act 2023 shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

15 November, 2023. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 21st November, 2023.
